**TASK-004**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/models/__init__.py`\n37:   - Package subpackage marker\n38: \n39: - [ ] **TASK-005**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/runtime/__init__.py`\n40:   - Re-export all runtime classes (PackRuntime, BuildRuntime, PublishRuntime, InvokeRuntime, StatusRuntime)\n41:   - Define `__all__` list\n42: \n43: - [ ] **TASK-006**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/services/__init__.py`\n44:   - Package subpackage marker with docstring\n45: \n46: - [ ] **TASK-007**: Create `cmd/cli/agentcube/operations/__init__.py`\n47:   - Placeholder module with docstring\n48: \n49: ### Phase 2: Metadata Models (`agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`)\n50: \n51: - [ ] **TASK-010**: Create `agentcube/services/metadata_service.py`\n52:   - Define package imports (pathlib, typing, yaml, pydantic)\n53: \n54: - [ ] **TASK-011**: Define `AgentMetadata` Pydantic model in `metadata_service.py`\n55:   - Field `agent_name: str` (required)\n56:   - Field `description: Optional[str]` (default: None)\n57:   - Field `language: str` (default: \"python\")\n58:   - Field `entrypoint: str` (required)\n59:   - Field `port: int` (default: 8080)\n60:   - Field `build_mode: str` (default: \"local\")\n61:   - Field `region: Optional[str]` (default: None)\n62:   - Field `version: Optional[str]` (default: None)\n63:   - Field `image: Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` (default: None)\n64:   - Field `auth: Optional[Dict[str, Any]]` (default: None)\n65:   - Field `requirements_file: Optional[str]` (default: \"requirements.txt\")\n66:   - Field `registry_url: Optional[str]` (default: \"\")\n67:   - Field `registry_username: Optional[str]` (default: \"\")\n68:   - Field `registry_password: Optional[str]` (default: \"\")\n69:   - Field `agent_endpoint: Optional[str]` (default: None)\n70:   - Field `workload_manager_url: Optional[str]` (default: None)\n71:   - Field `router_url: Optional[str]` (default: None)\n72:   - Field `readiness_probe_path: Optional[str]` (default: None)\n73:   - Field `readiness_probe_por